<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Recuperar acceso | LoginPro</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/favicon-loginpro.svg" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
      color: #1f2937;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      padding: 28px;
    }
    .brand img { height: 32px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; display: block; }
    h1 { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 24px; color: #111827; }
    p { margin-top: 8px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    form { margin-top: 20px; display: grid; gap: 14px; }
    .field label { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; font-weight: 600; }
    .field input {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .field input:focus { border-color: #4f46e5; }
    .btn {
      margin-top: 6px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #4f46e5;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 11px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #4338ca; }
    .error, .success {
      margin-top: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
    }
    .error {
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      background: #fef2f2;
      color: #b91c1c;
    }
    .success {
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      background: #f0fdf4;
      color: #166534;
    }
    .helper {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .helper a {
      color: #4f46e5;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <div class="brand">
      <img src="/public/logo-loginpro.svg" alt="LoginPro" />
    </div>
    <h1>Recuperar acceso</h1>
    <p>Usa el usuario, el código de recuperación entregado por dev/reclutador y define una nueva contraseña.</p>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if (success) { %>
      <div class="success"><%= success %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="post" action="/recover">
      <div class="field">
        <label for="username">Usuario</label>
        <input id="username" name="username" type="text" required autocomplete="username" value="<%= username %>" />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="recoveryCode">Código de recuperación</label>
        <input id="recoveryCode" name="recoveryCode" type="text" inputmode="numeric" autocomplete="one-time-code" required />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="newPassword">Nueva contraseña</label>
        <input id="newPassword" name="newPassword" type="password" autocomplete="new-password" minlength="6" required />
      </div>

      <button class="btn" type="submit">Actualizar contraseña</button>
    </form>

    <div class="helper">
      <a href="/login">Volver al login</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
